{"tid":88323,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鐘意肥媽？","createTime":"2017-01-20T14:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T14:53:09.000Z","uid":3066,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d8de47f7f1ae268b2d75cbe55f8a4eb64000f1","tid":88323,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Maria Cordero</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">肥媽 葡國國藉</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">瑪俐亞<br />\n1954年2月18日（62歲）<br />\n葡屬澳門</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑪俐亞，BBS，MH（葡萄牙語：Maria Cordero，1954年2月18日[4]－），人稱「肥媽」，土生葡人，具有華裔血統，是在澳門出生，在香港成長的著名歌手、美食評論家、節目主持人及演員。肥媽在1980年代出道。現時她仍活躍於娛樂圈，亦會熱心公益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/220612_1528a10a1a3f1fa764c3c567da73cbb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F220612_1528a10a1a3f1fa764c3c567da73cbb6.jpg&h=dd9df3b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f38e6ab7e467df9a720db19e6026edcf417b45fe","tid":88323,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/58GY155idFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F58GY155idFg&d=UErNqmWN9NC47ofRl3lGNWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=5cce1f5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/58GY155idFg</a>"},{"pid":"85d062d404fd8e69ee56498732bd4d9d689f26c0","tid":88323,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e812399642d3892a359d67009b39321b4980e9e","tid":88323,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"298775442ccee6bcf48672ca600b75d1ae200deb","tid":88323,"uid":58099,"like